      description: "Use when a Nectar build, dev server, or dashboard fails to start, errors out mid-build, or produces unexpected output. Walks through the canonical diagnosis commands (`nectar doctor`, `nectar check`, `nectar diagnostics`) and the common error â†’ fix recipes.",
